h4 Customization
p.-text
  | This component accepts a small number of visual changes. The numbering of the panels is optional, so you can omit
  | the <code>m-epanel__number</code> class elements. In this case, the active content will render with a not desired
  | margin, that can be removed with the <code>-ml--0</code> class.
