h3 State custom behavior
p.-text
  | The four expansion panel states behave very similar one from each other. Although you shouldn't, you may, 
  | for example, use footer element in a <code>pending</code> panel, or an
  | action button in an <code>active</code> panel.
p.-text
  | There are two main differences between them.
ol.-text
  li
    | The title will render in the brand color for the active panel, in soft gray for the disabled panel and black for
    | the other panel states.
  li Two hiding utility classes will hide content depending on the state.

